The market will close at 4:00 PM ET on November 18, 2022. The market will expire at the sooner of the first 7:00 PM ET after the release of the data, or one week after November 18, 2022.

Pursuant to the Kalshi Rulebook, the Exchange has modified the Source Agency and Underlying for indices markets. See the rules for more information.
